'''卡什提里亚什四世'''（{{lang-en|Kashtiliashu IV}}，约公元前1232年—约公元前1225年在位），[[加喜特|加喜特]][[国王|国王]]，<ref>Bertman,Stephen.（2005）. ''The Handbook to Life in Ancient Mesopotamia''.Oxford University Press,USA.ISBN 9780195183641.</ref>承袭[[沙噶拉克提·舒瑞亚什|沙噶拉克提·舒瑞亚什]]之位，尽管其统治短暂，仍有百余部相关的[[经济|经济]][[文献|文献]]传世至今。他统治时期曾經与[[亚述|亚述]]发生矛盾冲突，并遭到后者废黜。<ref name=bryce>{{ cite book | title = ''Letters of the great kings of the ancient Near East: the royal'' | url = https://archive.org/details/lettersgreatking00bryc | author = Trevor Bryce | publisher = Routledge | year = 2003 | page = [https://archive.org/details/lettersgreatking00bryc/page/11 11] }}</ref>

